Class GroundAtom

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.linqs.psl.model.atom.Atom
      • org.linqs.psl.model.atom.GroundAtom
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<GroundAtom>, Formula, SummationAtomOrAtom, FunctionTerm
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ObservedAtom, RandomVariableAtom

    public abstract class GroundAtom
extends Atom
implements Comparable<GroundAtom>, FunctionTerm
    An Atom with only GroundTerms for arguments. A GroundAtom has a truth value.
